00:58:13.066 --> 00:58:18.100
participate that they can have collaboration to start our programs.

00:58:18.100 --> 00:58:19.200
That will work.

00:58:25.233 --> 00:58:26.533
Q: Hi. Just, just one question from me.

00:58:26.533 --> 00:58:28.567
